685, 199.7541, 201.1887, 200.091, 199.455, 199.7373, 198.6906, 197.6067, 196.4791, 195.4892, 195.7315, 195.0244, 195.3506, 196.2735, 195.8805, 195.3209, 195.9842, 196.0177, 196.5135, 196.4892, 196.4043, 196.4466, 196.1142, 195.7628, 196.2597, 196.7236, 197.2501, 197.7377, 197.2281, 197.0158, 195.7744, 195.7674, 194.7105, 195.7562, 195.1818, 195.2423, 195.4939, 194.8951, 194.6473, 194.7664, 195.4691, 195.9605, 196.0269, 194.6125, 195.7318, 195.6767, 195.992, 196.9382, 196.2608, 194.1888, 193.9438, 192.4934, 191.297, 191.9292, 192.3047, 192.7744, 191.6058, 191.8516, 192.2302, 193.2275, 194.3171, 194.7918, 194.7307, 196.1402, 195.1045, 195.923, 196.6456, 198.129, 197.6914, 197.257, 196.5505, 196.9716, 197.6774, 198.8527, 198.9813, 198.3757, 199.5957, 200.2199, 200.7503, 200.7442, 200.179, 200.0634, 199.9177, 199.7407, 199.5781, 199.7711, 199.8367, 199.2527, 198.7517, 198.9742, 198.4145, 198.3238, 198.4666, 197.786, 198.0182, 198.7848, 197.8918, 198.8683, 198.6669, 199.0608, 198.7315, 197.6306, 198.7294, 198.4287, 198.6658, 199.466, 199.9086, 199.5685, 200.5417, 201.3698, 201.2402, 200.5047, 201.2264, 202.6088, 202.7987, 202.1901, 202.4132, 201.6196, 201.5578, 203.2387, 203.1777, 202.7458, 202.2046, 202.0899, 200.464, 203.5624, 202.5426, 202.6075, 202.8628, 204.4153, 204.6345, 203.2473, 203.4913, 205.5023, 204.6766, 203.98, 204.4858, 203.7458, 205.2288, 205.8498, 204.747, 204.3097, 204.9244, 203.534, 203.0008, 205.9536, 204.3945, 205.685, 205.8896, 204.0426, 206.4613, 206.0837, 205.5463, 206.429, 202.4587, 202.6472, 199.1023, 201.2207, 198.2266, 196.266, 195.9316], "summary_html": "<h1>铅基本面量化因子挖掘 -- 截面化推广</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原文研究了铅市场中再生铅与原生铅的价差机制：当铅价高企时，再生铅利润丰厚，供应弹性大，贴水出货挤占原生铅需求，压制价格；反之铅价低位时再生铅利润萎缩，供应收紧，原生铅需求增加，构成价格下沿支撑。这一\"利润驱动供应弹性→价差锚定震荡区间\"的逻辑，本质上是基本面均值回归的一个特例。</p>\n<p>由于原文使用的再生铅-原生铅价差数据（SMM外部数据）不可得，我们将核心逻辑拆解为三个可截面化推广的基本面因子： 1. <strong>基差因子（basis）</strong>: 高基差（backwardation）=库存紧张=做多，低基差（contango）=供应充裕=做空 2. <strong>库存变化率因子（inventory_cr）</strong>: 库存累积=需求弱=做空，库存消耗=需求强=做多 3. <strong>利润因子（profit_chg）</strong>: 高利润=供应扩张压力=做空，低利润=供应收缩=做多</p>\n<p>最终最优方案为基差+库存两因子等权组合的截面排名策略，利润因子因信号质量弱（Sharpe &lt; 0.3）被从组合中降权。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.35</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.64 / 1.11</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.52</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.0</span></td><td>1.7</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.4</span></td><td>1.2</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.13</span></td><td>1.13</td><td>0.91</td><td>1.37</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td>1.58</td><td>0.85</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.03</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.7</span></td><td>1.28</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 60 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 60 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>基差因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_norm}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{basis}_{i,t}}{\\text{close}_{i,t}}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_ma}_{i,t}^{W} = \\frac{1}{W}\\sum_{k=0}^{W-1} \\text{basis\\_norm}_{i,t-k}</div>\n<h3>库存变化率因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_cr}_{i,t}^{M} = \\frac{\\text{Inv}_{i,t}}{\\frac{1}{M}\\sum_{k=0}^{M-1}\\text{Inv}_{i,t-k}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Inv}</span> 优先使用 <code>inventory_21</code>，缺失时回退至 <code>receipt</code>，并做 forward-fill。</p>\n<h3>组合信号</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_{i,t} = \\text{rank}^{CS}(\\text{basis\\_ma}_{i,t}) + (1 - \\text{rank}^{CS}(\\text{inv\\_cr}_{i,t}))</div>\n<p>对 combo 再做截面排名，通过 <code>rank_to_continuous</code> 转为 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, +1]</span> 连续仓位信号。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>单因子basis最强(1.18)，profit极弱(0.08)，turnover=0.58</td><td>实现profit/inv/basis三因子+combo，无hold约束</td><td>Sharpe 1.18，但basis独大</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>加入rebalance_hold降低换手；basis+inv组合优于三因子</td><td>增加H5/H10持仓约束，2因子combo替代3因子</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: Sharpe 1.18→1.45，bi_basis_ma20_60_H10_raw最优</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>H10已不错，尝试更长持仓H15/H20；加inv_cr80窗口</td><td>扩展H15/H20+inv80网格，加CS归一化</td><td>Sharpe 1.45→1.47（CS归一化小幅提升）</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>基差是最强因子，利润因子在截面维度几乎无效（可能是因为利润数据更新频率低）</li>\n<li>库存变化率与基差互补，2因子组合稳定优于单因子</li>\n<li>rebalance_hold(H10-H15) 显著降低换手成本，提升净Sharpe</li>\n<li>截面标准化(CS)对连续信号有小幅提升</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个商品期货），需 basis/inventory 非空</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中 xinye 库存因子相关性 0.54（corr &gt; 0.5），但本策略 Sharpe(1.47) &gt; xinye(1.12)\n<p>- 2024-2025 年度 Sharpe 接近零，近期信号有效性减弱 - 利润因子截面信号弱，可能是数据质量问题（利润数据更新不及时） - 原文针对铅单品种（短期样本 Sharpe 3.22），全品种推广后 Sharpe 下降属预期</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INV_M</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>inventory change-rate lookback</td></tr><tr><td><code>BASIS_W</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>basis_norm MA window</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>SCALE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>rank_to_continuous scale</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.19s</li>\n</ul>"}